---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: Already Under
Description: April 4
---
Late by myself, in the boat of myself,
no light and no land anywhere,
cloudcover thick.

I try to stay just above the surface,
yet I am already under
and living within the ocean.
